FYI.  This could be quite important for us.  Through forming a tradinf co. we 
could be brokering deals on behalf of MSEB, without letting them off the hook.

In this manner we could be doing short term deals and increasing despatch 
from Dabhol or other MSEB marginal units.  Any money flowing from these sales 
should go into an escrow account that goes directly towards payment of DPC 
bills.

In this manner we would be increasing the payment ability of MSEB.

Regards,
Sandeep.
